{"tid":1918530,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Minecraft 樹窿Craft 伺服器/生存世界RPG/Skyblock","createTime":"2020-03-10T07:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T06:47:38.000Z","uid":197011,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe0d3646dc77ec496920360389de2e1475c4d7f","tid":1918530,"uid":197011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"伺服器地址: mc.hongkong.moe<br />\n版本：1.14.* - 1.15.2<br />\n正版驗證：Y<br />\n最大人數：100<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2uYZ9Zq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uYZ9Zq&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=33de0dda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2uYZ9Zq</a><br />\n必看指令Wiki: <a href=\"https://wiki.hongkong.moe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.hongkong.moe&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=55312c78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.hongkong.moe</a> 睇住玩，咩指令都識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">所有生存用指令前面要加/cmi 例如/cmi spawn，/cmi sethome</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSkyblock同生存世界完全分開 互不干擾 <br />\nRPG同生存世界係同一世界<br />\n<br />\n伺服器雖然唔多人，但長久穩定<br />\n啱各位養老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，Admin又好人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">保證冇小學雞同外掛，見到即ban <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n生存世界會膸機出現世界王，暫時有流浮山刀王 奧丁同哈帝斯<br />\n分別掉落唔同RPG裝備<br />\n<br />\n主城SPAWN點：打/cmi spawn 可返spawn<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gbQYryC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgbQYryC.png&h=cda6bd8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VkYaayx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVkYaayx.png&h=fc71bbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市集NPC：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MNXEoO0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMNXEoO0.png&h=6fd0a42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4e9SwGo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4e9SwGo.png&h=894db0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界王：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f1mEeT9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff1mEeT9.png&h=da7a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MkvjWDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMkvjWDy.png&h=ea46aae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原版冇嘅新物品：打/ia 可睇到合成表<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7i0V79w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7i0V79w.png&h=8aed8f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M3sUl3v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM3sUl3v.png&h=470f4341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uVzi3Pk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuVzi3Pk.png&h=b9cad79a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRPG裝備：世界王掉落<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/C63a4Er.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FC63a4Er.png&h=945b58a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ACXD86X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FACXD86X.png&h=c741d90c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZSbpDGa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZSbpDGa.png&h=ad4e647a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wCdryY8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwCdryY8.png&h=67e0ae84&s={SIZE}\" /><